{"tid":171716,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶檔吸金黃心穎餵食　馬國明直認：唔係普通朋友咁簡單","createTime":"2017-03-25T13:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T08:09:32.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df6cdcedf27aad5879165f7633f9c57f56f7d6e4","tid":171716,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/485715/xlarge/45da9bbe6559375b1ede2a0c62382964.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F485715%2Fxlarge%2F45da9bbe6559375b1ede2a0c62382964.jpg&h=5d17e0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n究竟馬國明與黃心穎是「真情侶，地下情」，還是「假情侶，有緋聞」，抑或「曖昧中，不確定」的關係呢？但是當新聞稿已寫上「緋聞馬國明黃心穎」時，我還應該當他們是緋聞嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/485716/xlarge/12081b1817c5c97cf69d28cf4af462aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F485716%2Fxlarge%2F12081b1817c5c97cf69d28cf4af462aa.jpg&h=11872033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「聽聞價錢好啲吖嘛。」馬國明在台上回答主持人問題說到。連馬國明都知道「情侶檔」合體出席活動的酬勞會比較高，似乎此次活動「含金量」也不少，不過有宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曲」之餘，馬明亦唱了一首「友情歲月」及「心願」，驚喜的是原來黃心穎歌喉真的不錯。隨後更有與人形公仔跳舞及製作窩夫環節，又讓心穎餵馬明食窩夫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/485721/xlarge/b4e94d8d50ee6267ed2ad16b9bde2bcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F485721%2Fxlarge%2Fb4e94d8d50ee6267ed2ad16b9bde2bcb.jpg&h=717328c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二人接受「香港01」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />餸畀你食？）「咁好難要求個女仔煮嘢畀自己食嘅。」心穎這個時候笑說：「佢依家要求緊我煮嘢畀佢食。」及後馬國明補充道：「我由細到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />畀個男仔食，佢哋關係就唔會係普通朋友咁簡單。」而問到緋聞中的他們會否繼續「情侶檔」出席活動時，心穎就搶答說：「嘩，最好吖。」馬國明接着補充道：「有錢搵梗係好啦⋯」啱嘅，可以見面之餘又可以搵錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/485724/xlarge/0f6803a8015f388c1c3cb13f534fcd2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F485724%2Fxlarge%2F0f6803a8015f388c1c3cb13f534fcd2e.jpg&h=96aaf120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不難發覺，大會刻意營造了情侶的感覺。當時人不介意之餘，公司又樂見多一對緋聞情侶，大眾亦喜歡這對「金童玉女」的組合，至於戀情真假與否，其實有關係嗎？"},{"pid":"e6371405fe4ec328112647ee8ce47318536227e5","tid":171716,"uid":7336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T17:30:30.000Z","msg":"中間啲字無啦啦加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcd98f5d41a0c16696cc613edca5e30a474ba8d","tid":171716,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"馬明係咪可以喺食賓賓PO出包膠"},{"pid":"6260c7c345a4326132282eb7902d4185eedb2532","tid":171716,"uid":42180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T17:37:38.000Z","msg":"馬明D答案毒到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係要提起自己老母"},{"pid":"610eec29a3e16195136153dd4926b7365821002a","tid":171716,"uid":48658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"中間d加密係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a479cc37121d3a5b05a2ed63d96b9020f875f3","tid":171716,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:04:45.000Z","msg":"你識加密但又唔識加埋朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aafc1c3ddcd337de861325d4c64217df6341fe1","tid":171716,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:13:37.000Z","msg":"朱千雪呢?朱千雪呢?!!!!!"},{"pid":"2d87030b351a4c391c3ad012242bad399e17bdc4","tid":171716,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中間啲字無啦啦加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B6VuJ30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih